reviews.review_text: Best Aud source Other than the crappy sounding 2nd set aud source available since 2010, this is the only aud of this show.   It sounds very good.  Hey, better late than never.  Thank you to all involved getting this up here.

thank you yes, as stated below, thanks for the new crowd source, it sounds very good.
Happy Trails...
